    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To SortoutCode! ‚ù§Ô∏è To change the label text size with the form group component using BootstrapVue.We are using the  component, to change‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To SortoutCode! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To change the label text size with the form group component using BootstrapVue.We are using the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;b-form-group></code> component, to change the label text size with the respective input size, we are going to use the <code class=\"language-text\">label-size</code> props in BootstrapVue.</p>\n<p>Today I am going to show you <strong><em>How you change the label text size with the form group component using BootstrapVue in VueJS?</em></strong></p>\n<p>Table of contains</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Setup the Vue.js</li>\n<li>Install the Bootstrap and BootstrapVue</li>\n<li>Create FirstComponent.vue and import it into App.js</li>\n<li>Change the label text size with a form group component</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start today‚Äôs tutorial <strong><em>How do I change the label text size with the form group component using BootstrapVue in VueJS?</em></strong></p>\n<h2>Setup the Vue.js</h2>\n<p>First, we have to install the Vue project, I had installed the vueJS in my system. If you haven‚Äôt installed or have any problem with installation you can follow this article, which will show you step by step process of installation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/blog/how-to-setup-vuejs-project/\" target=\"_BLANK\">How to Install the VueJS project?</a></p>\n<h2>Install the Bootstrap and BootstrapVue</h2>\n<p>First, we have to install the Vue project, I had installed the vueJS in my system. If you haven‚Äôt installed or have any problem with installation you can follow this article, which will show you step by step process of installation. In that article, I had also show you how to install BootstrapVue in your vue.js project step by step.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/blog/how-to-install-vue-bootstrap-in-vuejs/\" target=\"_BLANK\">How to install or configure vue-bootstrap in VueJS?</a></p>\n<h2>Create FirstComponent.vue and import it into App.js</h2>\n<p>Create the new component in the <code class=\"language-text\">src/components/</code> components folder. the component name is <code class=\"language-text\">FirstComponent.vue</code> and imported into the <code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code> file:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"app\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FirstComponent <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FirstComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./components/FirstComponent.vue\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"App\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">components</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    FirstComponent<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Change the label text size with the form group component</h2>\n<p>Using the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;b-form-group></code> component we are adding some structure to the form. Its purpose is to add the form control with a label and to provide help text and invalid/valid feedback text, as well as visual (color) contextual state feedback.</p>\n<p>We can change the label text size which matches the size of your form input(s). For that, we are going to use the <code class=\"language-text\">label-size</code> props. Values can be <code class=\"language-text\">sm</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">lg</code> for the small or large labels, respectively. Sizes work for both horizontal and non-horizontal form groups. Let‚Äôs see the code example:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">FirstComponent.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>container fluid<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>row<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>col md<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"6\"</span> offset<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>md<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"3\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Welcome to sortoutcode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>group label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Sitename with label small size\"</span> label<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sm\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>input v<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>model<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sitename\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>input<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>group<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>group label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Sitename with label medium size\"</span> label<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"md\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>input v<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>model<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sitename\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>input<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>group<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>group label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Sitename with label large size\"</span> label<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"lg\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>input v<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>model<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sitename\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>input<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>group<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>col<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>row<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>b<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>container<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"FirstComponent\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">data</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">sitename</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>For now, let‚Äôs check the output.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7129ed3e44